comments: Morris Sr. (LAC) makes contact with Embiid's (PHI) arm and contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) makes marginal contact to George's (LAC) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Green (PHI) and Morris Sr. (LAC) make incidental contact with each other pursuing the rebound.  Morris Sr. lands off-balance and Green reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball.
Embiid (PHI) and Jackson (LAC) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Rondo (LAC) makes marginal contact to Embiid's (PHI) front and he is able to move through the contact.
Embiid (PHI) moves laterally in Rondo's (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the loose ball.
Batum (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Simmons' (PHI) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Embiid (PHI) places a hand on Batum's (LAC) side and extends into him, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Green (PHI) legally contests George (LAC) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Simmons (PHI) places his arm to George's (LAC) front and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Morris Sr. (LAC) makes contact with Korkmaz's (PHI) backside and contact affects his shot attempt at the basket.
George (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Green's (PHI) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Batum (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Simmons' (PHI) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Green (PHI) makes marginal contact to Morris Sr.'s (LAC) arm after the release of his shot attempt at the basket.
Embiid (PHI) makes incidental contact with Rondo's (LAC) foot at the end of his drive and after the release of his pass.
Embiid (PHI) places his off-arm against Morris Sr. (LAC) and marginal contact occurs just before he receives the pass.
Embiid (PHI) slightly extends his arms against Morris Sr.'s (LAC) front off ball and disengages.
Batum (LAC) commits a take foul on Green (PHI).
Simmons (PHI) and George (LAC) engage and disengage with one another off ball .
Embiid (PHI) makes incidental contact with Zubac's (LAC) face as he disengages.
Green (PHI) is in a legal guarding position and marginal contact occurs as Morris Sr. (LAC) extends his leg to create contact during the jump shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact to Zubac's (LAC) backside and disengages as they pursue the loose ball.
Rondo (LAC) makes incidental foot contact with the loose ball as he attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Thybulle (PHI) and George (LAC) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
